opam-version: "2.0"
name: "stog-rdf"
version: "0.16.1"
synopsis: "Plugin for Stog. Define and query RDF graphs in rewrite rules."
description: """
This plugin allows to use RDF graphs to generate parts of
documents and to generate RDF graphs from elements in
documents."""
